==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dispend
<hw>Dis*pend"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[OF.
<ets>despendre</ets>, L. <ets>dispendere</ets> to weigh out, dispense;
<ets>dis-</ets> + <ets>pendere</ets> to weigh. See <er>Pension</er>,
<er>Spend</er>, and cf. <er>Dispense</er>.]</ety> <def>To spend; to lay
out; to expend.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Able to <qex>dispend</qex> yearly twenty pounds and above.</q>
<rj><qau>Fuller.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dispender</ent>⟦br⟧
